<view class="page">
  <view class="header">
    <text class="title">血氧饱和度</text>
    <picker mode="date" value="{{selectedDate}}" start="1900-01-01" end="{{today}}" bindchange="onDateChange">
      <view class="date-btn">{{selectedDate}}</view>
    </picker>
  </view>
  <view class="summary">
    <view class="big-val">{{currentVal||'--'}}%</view>
    <view class="stats-row">
      <view class="stat"><text class="stat-title">本日平均血氧</text><text class="stat-val">{{avgVal||'--'}}%</text></view>
      <view class="stat"><text class="stat-title">本日血氧范围</text><text class="stat-val">{{minVal||'--'}}-{{maxVal||'--'}}%</text></view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="chart-card">
    <canvas class="chart" canvas-id="spo2-chart"></canvas>
  </view>
  <view class="about">
    <text class="about-title">关于血氧</text>
    <text class="about-text">血氧饱和度（SpO2）是衡量血液中血红蛋白与氧气结合程度的医学指标，反映血液携氧能力，是呼吸循环功能的重要参数。成人动脉血氧饱和度正常为95%–99%，通常不低于94%为正常，低于90%可能提示低氧血症，需医疗关注。血氧饱和度的测量对于监测肺部氧合功能和血红蛋白的携氧能力至关重要。</text>
  </view>
  <view class="panel">
    <button class="primary" bindtap="startMeasure">手动检测</button>
    <button bindtap="viewHistory">查看历史</button>
  </view>
  <view wx:if="{{isMeasuring}}" class="measure-mask">
    <view class="circle"><text class="circle-text">{{measureProgress}}%</text><text class="circle-tip">正在测量血氧</text></view>
  </view>
</view>